textAfterTable: Profile BlackRock Emerging Markets Index Fund is a UCITS certified open-end fund incorporated in Ireland. The Fund aims to provide total return, taking into account both capital and income returns, which reflects the total return of the Global Emerging equity market. The fund aims to invest in a portfolio of equity securities of the MSCI Emerging Markets Index.
